revisions.rev:
{{Other uses|Air force (disambiguation)}}
This alphabetically arranged '''list of [[air force]]s''' identifies the current and historical names and [[roundel]]s for the military aviation arms of countries fielding an air component, whether an independent air force, a naval air arm, army aviation unit, or coast guard. At the end is a separate [[#Former countries and movements|list of no longer extant nations that once operated air forces]]. Country names in ''italics'' indicate that they are not generally recognized internationally as independent states but which nonetheless managed to field an active air service. For information on the size of air forces, see [[list of countries by size of armed forces]].

__NOTOC__
